To find the initial population, evaluate \(P(0)\):

\[
P(0)=\frac{68}{1+16e^{-0.28\cdot0}}
=\frac{68}{1+16\cdot1}
=\frac{68}{17}
=4.
\]

So there were 4 koi in the pond initially.

